First, consult the following table to determine your maximum stuff:

|Level|Experience Total|Max Base Atk|Feats Total*|Ability Boost?|Max Skill Ranks**|h
|!0| -1,000 XP| +3 (auto)| 3 feats| By sub-class| 4 ranks|
|!1st| 0 XP| +4| 4 feats|| 4 ranks|
|!2nd| 1,000 XP| +4| 4 feats|| 4 ranks|
|!3rd| 3,000 XP| +4| 5 feats|| 4 ranks|
|!4th| 6,000 XP| +4| 5 feats| +1 to one| 4 ranks|
|!5th| 10,000 XP| +5| 6 feats|| 5 ranks|
|!6th| 15,000 XP| +6/+1| 6 feats|| 6 ranks|
|!7th| 21,000 XP| +7/+2| 7 feats|| 7 ranks|
|!8th| 28,000 XP| +8/+3| 7 feats| +1 to one| 8 ranks|
|!9th| 36,000 XP| +9/+4| 8 feats|| 9 ranks|
|!10th| 45,000 XP| +10/+5| 8 feats| +1 to all| 10 ranks|
|!11th| 55,000 XP| +11/+6/+1| 9 feats|| 11 ranks|
|!12th| 66,000 XP| +12/+7/+2| 9 feats| +1 to one| 12 ranks|
|!13th| 78,000 XP| +13/+8/+3| 10 feats|| 13 ranks|
|!14th| 91,000 XP| +14/+9/+4| 10 feats|| 14 ranks|
|!15th| 105,000 XP| +15/+10/+5| 11 feats|| 15 ranks|
|!16th| 120,000 XP| +16/+11/+6/+1| 11 feats| +1 to one| 16 ranks|
|!17th| 136,000 XP| +17/+12/+7/+2| 12 feats|| 17 ranks|
|!18th| 153,000 XP| +18/+13/+8/+3| 12 feats|| 18 ranks|
|!19th| 171,000 XP| +19/+14/+9/+4| 13 feats|| 19 ranks|
